OL,3,CAlmost half of nurses in England plan
OL,4,Cto quit or are considering it, survey
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMore than seven in 10 nurses said the
OL,8,Fpressure has become too much to stand
OL,9,Fwhile two thirds said their level of
OL,10,Fpay failed to meet their level of
OL,11,Fresponsibility, skills and
OL,12,Fcontribution.
OL,14,FThe survey gathered opinions of more
OL,15,Fthan 11,000 nursing staff across the
OL,16,FUK's NHS, social care and independent
OL,17,Fsettings, and the participants were
OL,18,Fself selecting.
