OL,4,Cto quit or are considering it, survey
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe RCN carries out the survey every
OL,8,Ftwo years, and says the findings
OL,9,Fshould "concentrate the minds" of
OL,10,Fpoliticians ahead of .
OL,12,FBetween 2013 and 2023 the number of
OL,13,Fnursing staff reporting they were
OL,14,Funder too much pressure at work
OL,15,Fincreased from 59.3% to 71.1%.
OL,17,FThe number of nurses saying they are
OL,18,Ftoo busy to also increased from 56% to
OL,19,F65.9 over the same 10-year period.
