OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Poor staffing, stress, burnout, and
OL,8,Fmorale are apparent on a daily basis -
OL,9,Fcamaraderie gets us through most days.
OL,10,FI hope for a future where my children
OL,11,Fand the next generations have a safe
OL,12,FNHS," she added.
