OL,3,CAlmost half of nurses in England plan
OL,4,Cto quit or are considering it, survey
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe survey results also suggested .
OL,9,FAcross every health and care setting
OL,10,Fin the UK, nursing staff said they
OL,11,Ffelt demoralised by pay that fails to
OL,12,Fmatch their levels of training,
OL,13,Feducation, skills and responsibilities.
OL,15,FIn recent years the dissatisfaction
OL,16,Fwith pay among nursing staff has
OL,17,Fintensified - only two in ten think
OL,18,Ftheir pay level or band is
OL,19,Fappropriate, halving from four in ten
OL,20,F(44%) in 2015.
