OL,4,Cto quit or are considering it, survey
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FWorking under pressure is also having
OL,8,Fan impact on nurses' personal lives.
OL,9,FMore than eight in ten (85%) admitted
OL,10,Fto working while ill during 2023 and
OL,11,Ffewer than a third reported being
OL,12,Fhappy with their work-life balance `
OL,13,Fthe lowest score recorded since 2013.
OL,15,FA senior nurse working in an acute
OL,16,Ftrust in the South of England said:
OL,17,F"Sometimes I arrive home depleted
OL,18,Fwithout energy to even look after
OL,19,Fmyself and I wonder if this is normal."
