OL,7,FThe RCN is asking the government to
OL,8,Finvest in the nursing profession and
OL,9,Fsubstantially lift pay over the coming
OL,10,Fyears to boost recruitment and
OL,11,Fretention across all health and care
OL,12,Fsettings.
OL,14,FThe last decade has seen nursing staff
OL,15,Fgrapple with "" as successive
OL,16,Fgovernments "fail to invest in the
OL,17,Fprofession", Professor Pat Cullen, RCN
OL,18,Fgeneral secretary and chief executive
OL,19,Fsaid.
