OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"The picture for nursing may look
OL,8,Fbleak, but as a general election
OL,9,Fapproaches, politicians have a chance
OL,10,Fto chart a better course. Our
OL,11,Fprofession is fundamental to building
OL,12,Fa healthy society and economy, but it
OL,13,Fcannot do that with its hands tied
OL,14,Fbehind its back.
