OL,3,CAlmost half of nurses in England plan
OL,4,Cto quit or are considering it, survey
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"For those wishing to form the next
OL,8,Fgovernment, this report should
OL,9,Fconcentrate minds. Patients and
OL,10,Fnursing staff should not have to keep
OL,11,Fsuffering for politicians to pay
OL,12,Fattention and take action. The next
OL,13,Fdecade must be better than the last."
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,16,FHealth and Social Care responded to
OL,17,Fthe report by saying: "We hugely value
OL,18,Fthe work of NHS nurses and remain
OL,19,Fcommitted to supporting the career
OL,20,Fdevelopment and wellbeing of all NHS
OL,21,Fstaff."
